File:   90-i2cfix.conf

Destination location:  /etc/X11/xorg.conf.d 

Fixes i2c errors when using nvidia driver with certain cards (e.g. GTX660Ti)

File:  95-my_i2c.rules
Location: /etc/udev/rules.d

